reviewText: A great double feature with bruce willis at his best as he will becomeone of the all time best action movie actor of all time.
hostage is one of my favorites movies, the set up is terrible but to me is like an extra. The quality is great with the bluray

OF THE TWO MOVIES, I LIKED  "HOSTAGE" BETTER. THE OTHER ONE "SET UP" NOT SO MUCH, BUT STILL DECENT. WILLIS DID A GOOD JOB AND PRETTY GOOD ACTION, BUT OF COURSE THIS IS NO "DIE HARD"!
I'M GLAD TO SEE HIM, WHEN HE DOES DIFFERENT PARTS.

IT WAS BAD.  TOO BLOODY.  THE STORY LINE WAS STUPID.  NOT THE USUAL BRUCE WILLIS TYPE OF MOVIE.
WOULD NOT RECOMMEND
